    <label>Terminatrix</label>
    <description>The Terminatrix (T-X) is designed to not only terminate humans but also rogue Terminators reprogrammed by the Resistance, an "anti-terminator terminator". It is a composite of the T-800 and T-1000, a solid endoskeleton covered with a liquid metal "mimetic polyalloy", allowing it to take the shape of any humanoid it touches. Because it is only coated in this material, it is possible to remove it from the endoskeleton using immensely strong magnetic force, such as that from a cyclic particle accelerator.</description>
